{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a back formed on four-- from four locks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it took four people and a navigator with a very, very long ore, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we came to the end, it took, you see, a whole day over the river.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it-- it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we came to the end, we found out there's a mobilization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a mobilization.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we met another couple from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was impossible to get a bus or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in partnership, we hired a taxi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that they were [? ferriers. ?] And they were driving with us along the mountain pass, you see, amongst the Jewish villages to buy sheepskin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that was the center of cheap sheepskin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you see, that was a very good experience because we saw so many township.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we saw shops, you know, that may-- so on one side was a Jewish bar or something, inn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on this other side there was a Christian firm you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the same day, we went to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let us out on-- at the railway station on the [INAUDIBLE] Street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- waited for something, and we got ourselves into a-- so a very packed train going up north.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And took us two days or so to come to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We see on the way-- we saw that most of the tracks were busy with army, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we came back, you see, that is end of August.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we went to the office, and [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Helena ?] wasn't [INAUDIBLE] [? little ?] for-- [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Helena-- ?] Lola, my wife, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
